类 GameCover

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameCover
  • public class GameCover
extends java.lang.Object
    The cover of the Game, including the choice of modes, and you can also learn the rules about the game by clicking help button, and the cover also provides the choice of the number of enemies in the mode of human vs computers, this cover provides a link between the users and game
